title: The One Where AJ Gibson & Emile Ennis Jr Confess Their Mess to Lala
description:
Ocean Kent is a frickin’ baby genius! She waves at everyone and had a great time at Teddi Mellencamp’s 2-year-old daughter’s birthday party! The preschool schmooze has started and Hartford and Ocean will go together. Period. And AJ and Emile join the podcast to tell the sweet story of their relationship, talk about the origin of their podcast, “Confess Your Mess,” share details about their upcoming nuptials and the difficulties of planning a destination wedding during a pandemic, and offer advice to young queer kids struggling in their small towns and communities. They also spill the tea on their personal coming out journeys, navigating Hollywood, and the work they do for the LGBTQ+ community.
